<H1>Using an editor</H1>

<OL>
<LI><P>Customise the mail program to 
<A HREF="custom1.html">use the editor</A> of your choice.</P></LI>
<LI><P>Use the editor's commands to insert the file
at the point in the mail message where you want to
include it.</P>

<P>Both the <A HREF="../vi/six.2.html">vi</A> and 
<A HREF="../emacs/index.html">emacs</A> editors provide this facility.</P></LI>
</OL>

